Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:16.74,Title,,0,0,0,,The Liar, Uncle Boulder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the fragment back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I clearly saw Wolffy run this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the fragment back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be on my way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, have you seen Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A stupid-looking, useless-looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,no-good-qualities-looking wolf that passed through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there fur on your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s actually a sweater I’m wearing underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so cold today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it’s… summer, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, I’ve been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you’re sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to see a doctor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a fish have fur?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That was obviously just Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you’re a little too gullible, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, this was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make sure to find another Ocean Star fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gem is really beautiful;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,could you lend it to me for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need one gem,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and this crown will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a unique crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I made it out of scrap materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask what you’re making this crown for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter is taking part in a Children’s Day performance;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,this is her first time being the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just that she’s still missing a complete crown,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so I’d like to borrow your gem for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems like it’d be a hard thing to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since gem is truly very important,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are you sure you’ll only borrow it for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one day is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You lended the fragment to Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Uncle Boulder was sent by Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw Uncle Boulder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,give a fragment to Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,why were you gullible yet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s definitely a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry and take the fragment back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,did he leave you any contact information?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He left me a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s go find that liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like he’s a good dad;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he’s probably not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure he’ll return it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should wait one more day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that Uncle Boulder wouldn’t keep his promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve got to track him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is too big;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how are we supposed to find Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s get out and ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you know Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know that liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you know Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you guys looking for that liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder really is a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask how exactly he lied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t speak of such a painful memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder… he…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I found where Uncle Boulder lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But this place doesn’t even have the house from the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There can only be one reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we’ve gone to the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder gave me a fake location?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder is a liar from start to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have been so gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the fragment wouldn’t have been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t let me see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to tell him to hand over the actual location!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Uncle Boulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out they really are working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys bullying me for not having Sirius around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please keep seated while we are in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve finally got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m returning this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my fragment you’re holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you give Tibbie’s fragment to Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here’s what happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you lend me this gem for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my treasure, you know;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how could I just lend it to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you with Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his stomach wasn’t feeling so well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and asked me where the nearest toilet was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But how come we couldn’t find your house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when we went to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a waterspout came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and took my daughter as fast as I could to find shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,while our house was destroyed by the waterspout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I was looking for a new place to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was late in returning the gem as I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so glad that you weren’t a liar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not have lied to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why does everyone say that you’re a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I’m a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Says who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m asking you once more, so say it out loud;
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,am I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie Swaddle, I’ve already said it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really look rather…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,mediocre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mediocre?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m also asking you once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I’m tall and powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sturdy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you really aren’t all that tall and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When they said “liar,” this is what they meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you guys for helping me rebuild my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem; it’s the least we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Boulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you collecting all that garbage for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t garbage;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they’re all treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they’re all other people’s scrap materials,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they can be turned into new things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,after recycling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome; that way, it won’t go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, if there’s anything you guys need,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help you guys make it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can make Paddi a little more industrious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
